<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=203307">Craegor Icewulf 47 Warrior</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zhuas>Zhuas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#333333>(12/9/02 4:48:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1698.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: .::Ecstatic Spell Pricing::.</span><hr size=1> Heh well that's true, but still 20k is a lot. I'm not saying i don't want the spells though, *shrug* oh well.. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=amitan>Amitan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 33<br> <font color=#333333>(12/9/02 11:49:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1698.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.online.no/~ste-helg/artimages/sigpic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: .::Ecstatic Spell Pricing::.</span><hr size=1> 20k? hehe seen spells sell for WAY more. <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Sage Enzo the Arch Mage<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Mith Marr</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
