&quot;Long Have I Desired to Look Upon the Kings of Old, My Kin&quot;</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ailees>Ailees</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ikebana-toulouse.com/maitres/ailees.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 783<br> <font color=#333333>(12/9/02 12:39:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1698.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: .::Ecstatic Spell Pricing::.</span><hr size=1> well I never had 20K money in my chest, then it is not a problem for me :; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zacatac>Zacatac</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 1494<br> <font color=#333333>(12/9/02 5:34:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1698.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: .::Ecstatic Spell Pricing::.</span><hr size=1> If I was a 61 mage who didn't have Epic pet, 20k for the 61 Air pet would be a definate purchase.  Some of the other stuff isn't worth that much to me though.  Summond focus items, elemental barrier, etc. will need to be priced quite a bit lower to interest me.<br>
Saw summoned choker and mantle for sale at 9k each.  Not going to bother with those until they drop to about 3k (or I get them myself).<br>
<br>
 <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4796"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Baron Zacatac Soulwanderer</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ithryn>Ithryn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 151<br> <font color=#333333>(12/10/02 6:53:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1698.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: .::Ecstatic Spell Pricing::.</span><hr size=1> Pay what you want, but if you play much at all, you'll eventually get them for free.<br>
<br>
These spells aren't like Kunark/Velious/Luclin dropped spells, where you often have to go to specific zones and kill some very tough mobs to get certain ones.  They also are nowhere near the difficulty of getting your epic pet.<br>
<br>
A little patience and grouping in PoP is all it takes to get these spells.  I think 20Kpp is rediculous... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hairyblue>Hairyblue</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#333333>(12/10/02 8:41:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1698.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   55 spells and over</span><hr size=1> The pricing and availability of the 55 plus spells are terrible.  I have been after my 55 spells for 2 weeks now.  Either the bazaar has the spell and it's 3 k or more or they don't have it at all.  I dont' have 3 k to spend of spells.  <br>
<br>
Some of the spells I don't even want.  Like the Pouch of summoned throwing stars.  But I would like Burn out 4 and the new DoT for sure.  I'm sorta interesed in the Rage of Zomm spell too.<br>
<br>
My only opion is to keep saving up and hopefully the spells I need will appear.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=epicureofquellious>EpicureOfQuellious</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 120<br> <font color=#333333>(12/10/02 9:26:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1698.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 55 spells and over</span><hr size=1> coth was going for 25pp the other day on quellious in the bazaar.  Spent 6k on it 6 months or so ago.<br>
Its difficult  to ask when people think the spells will come down in price.  Fact is: the price is directly related to the ratio of supply to demand.<br>
Problem is, who the heck knows what kind of supply we are facing when the drop rates of spells have been adjusted (read nerfed) by VI and people beg for rates to increase (hey sometimes they listen!).<br>
<br>
What is known for sure (well almost) is that they WILL come down sooner or later.  Sooner or later depending on the drop rates in currently poplulated zones, the drop rates in zones that are just now being broken in, any adjustment Vi makes to the rates, the amount of mages on your server, the efficiency of your servers guilds/groups to clear mobs, the need/utility of each spell, and the price of Fish and Chips at The Iron Kettle in Creston BC.<br>
<br>
On the other hand, price won't be an issue if you are fortunate to get the drop and turn in yourself.<br>
<br>
<br>
 <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=65160&amp;resize=true" target="top">Epicure</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nanamarinfernostorm>Nanamar Infernostorm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 593<br> <font color=#333333>(12/11/02 2:12:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1698.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 55 spells and over</span><hr size=1> I sold a copy of Ward of Xegony for 10k VERY fast, and a copy of Servant of Marr the person felt guilty for only giving me a bio orb (I was looking for more), but I knew the guy and he was a cool guy, it just depends on what people sell for on your server.  No mage spell goes over 15-20k on Fennin ro but some classes have spells for Way more.  NM Only 60 pet heal goes for more <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   No one selling 63+ spells yet though <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=386526" target="top">Master Nanamar Infernostorm</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Tunare's Arch Mage of the 65th Summoning<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.bloodofhonor.waxscript.com/" target="top">Blood of Honor</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Fennin Ro<br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kilmir123>Kilmir123</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.lowlandelites.net/vb/avatar.php?userid=13&dateline=1034772585" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 123<br> <font color=#333333>(12/11/02 10:15:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1698.topic&index=10>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 55 spells and over</span><hr size=1> Got Black Steel for 10k and am buying my way through my 61-62 spells for about 3k-5k each (the decent ones, I got all the crappy ones via parchments already <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :\ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":\"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ). <br>
<br>
Haven't seen 62 water yet and am waiting for the 3 copies of BO5 to drop at or below 5k (this morning 2 at 8k, one at 7500 in the bazaar) <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .<br>
